{
  "resume_text": "Mr. Shihao Lai\n1210 S INDIANA AVE\nCHICAGO, IL 60605\n(224) 647-5878\nslai8@artic.edu\nEducation\nJULY 2025 - PRESENT\nSchool of the Art Institute of Chicago, US - Master of Design\n● Major: Designed Objects.\n● Research Focus: Toy Design.\nSEPTEMBER 2020 - JUNE 2024\nZhengzhou University, China - Bachelor of Engineering\n● Major: Industrial Design.\n● Extracurriculars: Student Union, Propaganda Department Illustrator.\nExperience\nMARCH 2025 - JUNE 2025\nAlpha Group, China - Product Designer Internship\n● Conducted sample supervision for multiple product lines.\n● Made alternate color schemes for action figures.\n● Drew three-view drawings.\nMAY 2024\nZhengzhou University Industrial Design Graduation Exhibition, China - Exhibitor\n● Responsible for setting up, maintaining, and dismantling my boot at the exhibition.\nAwards\nAUGUST 2023\n11th National College Art & Design Awards, First-class Prize of Henan Division\nSkills\n● Software: Rhino, Keyshot, Adobe Illustrator, Zbrush, Procreate\n● Language: Chinese (Native), English (Fluent), Japanese (N3)\n● Hobbies: Illustration, Manufacturing plastic kits, Clay sculpting, Miniature model painting\n\n",
  "script_text": "1: 我一定是被诅咒了\nI must be cursed\n2: 我只是个小人物做着些微不足道的工作\nI am just a nobody doing some trivial job\n3: 而那些大人物挥挥手就改变了整个世界的构造的时候\nWhen those Somebody wave their hands, they can change the entire structure of the universe\n4: 正在穿越亚空间与现实宇宙边缘的人就遭殃了\nThose who are traversing the edge between Unspace and the physical universe will suffer\n5: 现在我的火种无法回到物理宇宙了\nNow my spark cannot return to the physical universe\n6: 我听说过有一个组织会专门帮助迷失在亚空间的倒霉蛋\nI've heard of an organization that helping unfortunate souls who get lost in Unspace\n7: 也许终究只是传说罢了\nPerhaps it's just a Story after all\n8: 我在这里太久了，亚空间的环境已经开始侵蚀我的机体\nI've been here for too long, the Unspace has begun to erode my body\n9: 然而无尽的孤独并不是最可怕的，这里还有着更加的古老邪恶的存在\nFar worse than a mere eternity of solitude, There is a collection of ancient evil\n10: 如果丧失理智的话，身体就会被彻底溶解\nIf one loses their mind, their body will be completely dissolved\n11: 到那时，就没有什么能从古神手里保护你的了…\nBy then, nothing will be able to protect you from the Elder god…\n12: 为了加强我的精神力，我只能用智者战士的技术缩小我的身体\nTo Amplify my mental faculty, I have to shrink my body with BrainMaster technology\n13: 虽然这并不能阻止溶解，但是现在我能通过自己的意志重新固化那些部分\nAlthough this cannot prevent dissolution, I can now re-solidify those parts through my own will\n14: 这也只是缓兵之计\nThis is just a temporary solution.\n15: 我不知道我还能撑多长时间，我已经开始出现幻听了。一定是那些被邪神折磨的灵魂，在叫我\n加入他们…\nI don't know how much longer I can hold on. I've started experiencing hallucinations. It must be\nthe sparks tortured by the evil gods, beckoning me to join them…\n16: 但是在那之中，有一个声音和我的很像。它说它能帮助我。But among them, there was a\nvoice that sounded very similar to mine. It claimed it could help me.\n17: 讲道理这种情况下怎么可能相信这种话，但是我还有什么其他的办法吗？\nLogically, how could I possibly believe such words in this situation? But what other options did I\nhave?\n18: 在它的指引下，我找到了一块金属。\nUnder its guidance, I found a piece of metal.\n19: 这东西的成分…居然和亥索龙，那种吞噬时间和空间的野兽一致！那是一种高维生物，我不\n敢想象是什么东西让这种生物破了皮\n\nThe composition of this metal... is consistent with Hytherion, the beast that devours time and\nspace! That’s a hyper-dimensional creature, and I can’t imagine what could make such a\ncreature to get scraped\n20: 如果我能控制这种金属，也许我能在更高的纬度找到帮助我的方法！但这种生物的意识存在\n于每一个细胞中，我不能冒被它反噬的风险。\nIf I can control this metal, perhaps I can find a way to help me at a higher dimension! But the\nconsciousness of this creature exists in every cell, and I cannot risk being devoured by it.\n21: 在这金属里，居然存有一项技术的信息。Genetronic Translink! 利用亚空间通信技术远程驱动\n无火种的身体，这正是我所需要的。\nIn this metal, there actually exists information about a technology. Genetronic Translink! Utilizing\nUnspace communication technology to remotely drive a sparkless body, this is exactly what I\nneed.\n22: 这事真是越来越蹊跷了，但就像我说的，我没有太多选择了。\nThe whole thing is getting more and more mysterious, but as I said, I don't have many options.\n23: 我不确定以我的技术水平能否完美的再现这项技术，但是目前为止的实验成果都让我满意。\n是时候进入实践阶段了。\nI'm not sure if I can perfectly reproduce this technology with my skill, but the experimental\nresults so far have been satisfactory. It's time to move on to the practical stage.\n24:我只要将gt原件接上这块金属，它应该就能根据我的意志变成我想要的样子。\nI just need to connect the GT System to this metal, and it should be able to transform into the\nshape I want according to my will.\n25: 不…不对…看在天尊的面子上\nNo... This isn't right... In the name of the Primus…\n26: 它本应该变成…我的模样…\nIt’s supposed to be… in my image…\n27: 十年后\nten years later\n28: 哈哈，你说这些谁懂啊，这堆设定都多少年没人提过啦\nLOL, who would understand what you're saying? No one has mentioned these settings for years\n29: 你现在又能打破第四面墙了？为什么你就不能帮我解决我的问题呢？\nCan you break the fourth wall now? Why can't you help me solve my problem?\n30: 又不是这么用的\nIt’s not how it works\n31: 该死的，要是我操纵那具身体说不定早就解决了\nScrap, if I had controlled that body, I might have solved it long ago\n32: 把你给能的，要是你真这么能干，当初就不会出错了\nShow-off, If you are really that good, you wouldn't make mistakes in the first place.\n33: 结果搞到现在，还需要用我的右眼来当导航仪…等等，我好像感觉到什么东西\nAnd now, we still need to use my right eye as a navigator... Wait, I feel something.\n34: 如果我从你那里接收到的感觉没错，那我们就不再需要每次都把你的眼睛拆下来了\nIf the feeling I receive from you is correct, then we don't need to take your eye off every time.\n\n",
